where \eqn{s^2_{jg}} is the sample variance of item \eqn{j} in group \eqn{g} (using divisor \eqn{N_g-1}).
Then \eqn{CSEM(g) = \sqrt{\widehat{\sigma}^2_{E(cond)}(g)}}.

